OL,3,C'Lifeline' village bus axed after
OL,4,C20mph review to be 'temporarily
OL,5,Creinstated'
OL,7,FResidents in a Denbighshire village
OL,8,Fare vowing "not to give up" their
OL,9,Ffight to get their local bus fully
OL,10,Freinstated after the Llandegla stop
OL,11,Fwas removed from the timetable.
OL,13,FBut Denbighshire County Council says a
OL,14,F'temporary solution' has now been
OL,15,Ffound. It's had approval from all
OL,16,FNorth Wales authorities to use a
OL,17,Fportion of this year's Bus Transition
OL,18,FFunding to assist with the change made
OL,19,Fto this service.
