OL,3,C'Lifeline' village bus axed after
OL,4,C20mph review to be 'temporarily
OL,5,Creinstated'
OL,7,FA 'temporary' minibus will now be
OL,8,Fprovided to run the timetable through
OL,9,Fto the end of May.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the local authority
OL,12,Fsaid: "We have worked alongside
OL,13,FArriva, the Welsh Government and other
OL,14,FNorth Wales local authorities to
OL,15,Fsupport a temporary solution for this
OL,16,Ftransport route.
OL,18,F"This arrangement will be reviewed at
OL,19,Fthe end of May."
