OL,7,FCouncillor Gwyneth Dillon, from
OL,8,FLlandegla Community Council, says the
OL,9,Fservice is key to the "wellbeing of
OL,10,Fthe whole community."
OL,12,FShe told ITV Wales: "It's a step in
OL,13,Fthe right direction but locals in the
OL,14,Fvillage would like the bus service
OL,15,Fcompletely reinstated."
