OL,7,FThe bus service has been described as
OL,8,Fa "lifeline" to many by Darren Millar,
OL,9,FConservative MS for Clwyd West, who
OL,10,Fraised the matter in the Senedd and
OL,11,Fhas released a statement on his
OL,12,Fwebsite.
OL,14,F"Obviously, it is a concern that the
OL,15,Fservice will run until May 31st only,
OL,16,Fwhen there will be a further review of
OL,17,Fservices.
